# EVA AI Frontend - Cursor Rules

## ESSENTIAL PROJECT RULES

### Node Version
- Use Node 18.x or 20.x only
- Run `nvm use 20.11.0` if needed

### Tech Stack
- React 18 + TypeScript 4.9.5
- TailwindCSS for styling
- Zustand for state management
- React Hook Form for forms

### Development Commands
```bash
npm run start:no-lint    # Start without linting
npm run build           # Production build
npm run clean-install   # Fix dependency issues
```

### Code Standards
- Functional components only (no class components)
- Follow existing patterns in neighboring files
- Test builds before committing changes

### Quick Fixes
- Build fails: `npm run clean-install`
- Node issues: `nvm use 20.11.0`
- Emergency: `./emergency-fix.sh`